properties.headline: Air Quality Alert issued January 22 at 10:52PM EST by NWS Gray ME
properties.description:
..Air quality alert is in effect until 10 PM Saturday...

The New Hampshire Department of Environmental Services has issued
an air quality action day for the following counties...

Cheshire.

THE NEW HAMPSHIRE DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL SERVICES IS PREDICTING
UNHEALTHY AIR QUALITY FOR SENSITIVE GROUPS IN CHESHIRE COUNTY,
ESPECIALLY POPULATED VALLEY AREAS, THROUGH SATURDAY. CHILDREN,
OLDER ADULTS, OR ANYONE WITH HEART OR LUNG DISEASE WHO ARE IN
THESE AREAS SHOULD LIMIT PROLONGED EXERTION.
